# ðŸ½ï¸ Restaurant Menu Web App  

A fully responsive, real-time restaurant ordering web app built with **Supabase** and **vanilla JavaScript**.  
Customers can browse meals, add to cart, view categories, choose order type (Dine-in / Takeaway), and place orders directly via **WhatsApp**.  
The admin dashboard updates the frontend in **real time** â€” when meals are added, edited, or archived, the menu instantly updates without reloading.  

---

## ðŸš€ Features  

- âœ… **Dynamic Menu Display** â€” Meals fetched from Supabase and grouped by category  
- ðŸ” **Real-time Sync** â€” Instantly reflects added, updated, or archived meals  
- ðŸ›’ **Cart System** â€” Add, remove, or adjust items with live totals  
- ðŸ’¬ **WhatsApp Order Flow** â€” Sends order summary directly to restaurantâ€™s WhatsApp  
- ðŸŒ— **Light/Dark Mode** â€” Theme toggle with persistent state  
- ðŸ” **Category Tabs** â€” Filter meals instantly by category  
- âš¡ **Optimized Caching** â€” Faster load times via local caching  
- ðŸ“± **Responsive Layout** â€” Works smoothly on mobile, tablet, and desktop  

