## ðŸ’¬ WhatsApp Integration

Orders are sent directly to your WhatsApp.
To update your restaurant number, change this line in the script:

```js
window.open(`https://wa.me/234XXXXXXXXXX?text=${encodeURIComponent(waMessage)}`, '_blank');
```

---

## ðŸ§  Developer Notes

* Archiving a meal in the admin panel hides it from the menu **in real time**.
* Adjust caching duration inside your JS file:

  ```js
  const CACHE_DURATION = 5 * 60 * 1000; // 5 minutes
  ```
* Real-time updates handled by Supabase:

  ```js
  supabase
    .channel('public:meals')
    .on('postgres_changes', { event: '*', schema: 'public', table: 'meals' }, loadMeals)
    .subscribe();
  ```

